Ask HN: Would a “War Olympiad” end the war in Ukraine?
text:
A "War Olympiad" would allow countries to compete with their actual military hardware and best troops without killing anyone.

In this way, countries like Russia could gain the respect of the world without invading any countries.

P.S. This Olympiad would not decide any wars. It's just a way to show the world just how powerful your military is.
